<para style="p">

  <verse number="17" style="v" />Be imitators of me, brothers. Closely watch those who are walking by the example that you have in us.

  <verse number="18" style="v" />Many are walking—those about whom I have often told you, and now I am telling you with tears—as enemies of the cross of Christ.

  <verse number="19" style="v" />Their destiny is destruction. For their god is their belly, and their pride is in their shame. They think about earthly things.
